,{"width":2000,"height":1125,"file_path":"/pnDWKTRmuwqNtPMrfwdmmdweuby.jpg","iso_639_1":"xh","iso_3166_1":"XH","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T03:49:12.908+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":134,"tagline":"Welcome the incarnation of Dewi Asih…","homepage":"","overview":"Alana discover the truth about her origin: she’s not an ordinary human being. She may be the gift for humanity and become its protector as Sri Asih. Or a destruction, if she can’t control her anger."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sri Ashi ဇာတ်ကားဟာ အင်ဒိုနီးရှားစူပါဟီးရိုးဇာတ်ကားတစ်ကားဖြစ်ပါတယ်။ဒီဇာတ်ကားကို R.A Kosasih ရေးသားထားတဲ့ Sri Ashi၊ ဂန္တဝင်အင်ဒိုနီးရှားရုပ်ပြစာအုပ်ကိုပြင်ဆင်ပြီးlive-action ရိုက်ကူးထားခြင်းဖြစ်ပါတယ်။ ဒီဇာတ်ကားဟာဆိုရင် BCU (Bumilangit Cinema Universe) ရဲ့ Gundala (2019) အပြီး ဒုတိယမြောက်ထွက်ရှိလာတဲ့ကားပဲဖြစ်ပါတယ်။ ဇာတ်လမ်းအကျဉ်းလေးကတော့ အယ်လ်လန်နာဟာ သူမရဲ့အဖေနဲ့ အမေကိုသေဆုံးစေခဲ့တဲ့မီးတောင်ပေါက်ကွဲမှုအတွင်းမှာ မွေးဖွားလာခဲ့ပါတယ်။ သူမဟာ သူမရဲ့ ဒေါသစိတ်ကြောင့် အမြဲ အခက်အခဲတွေကိုအမြဲကျော်လွှားနိုင်ခဲ့တယ် အောင်နိုင်ခဲ့တယ်ဆိုတာကို နားမလည်ခဲ့ပေမယ့် အဲ့ဒီ့ဒေါသစိတ်ကို အမြဲတိုက်ထုတ်ဖို့ ကြိုးစားခဲ့ပါတယ်။ အဲ့နောက်မှာတော့ ချမ်းသာတဲ့ အမျိုးသမီးတစ်ယောက်ဟာ သူမကို သာမန်ဘဝလေးမှာပဲ နေထိုင်နိုင်ဖို့အတွက်မွေးစားခဲ့ပါတယ်။ ဒါပေမယ့် အယ်လ်လန်နာ အရွယ်ရောက်လာတဲ့အခါ သူမဟာသာမန်လူသားတစ်ယောက်မဟုတ်ကြောင်း သူမရဲ့ မူလဇာစ်မြစ် အမှန်တရားကို ရှာဖွေတွေ့ရှိသွားခဲ့ပါတယ်။ ဒီနောက်မှာတော့ ရန်သူတွေ အများကြီးပေါ်ပေါက်လာသလို သူဘယ်လို ရင်ဆိုင်ဖြေရှင်းမလဲဆိုတာကိုတော့"},"name":"","iso_639_1":"my","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Burmese"},{"data":{"title":"Nữ Chiến Binh Sri Asih","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ở Sri Asih, người ta kể rằng một cô gái tên Alana đã bị buộc phải trở thành cư dân của một trại trẻ mồ côi sau một sự kiện khủng khiếp khiến cô bị chia cắt khỏi cha mẹ ruột của mình kể từ khi cô được sinh ra. Alana sau đó được một người phụ nữ tên là Sarita nhận nuôi. Dưới sự dạy dỗ của Sarita, Alana trở thành một võ sĩ đáng gờm, để kiểm soát cơn giận dữ bí ẩn đã ám ảnh cô từ khi còn nhỏ. Sự cứng rắn của Alana khơi gợi sự tò mò của Mateo, một thanh niên giàu có du côn, con trai duy nhất của một người đàn ông đầy tham vọng tên là Prayogo. Một cuộc chiến được dàn dựng không theo thỏa thuận sau đó trở thành khởi đầu cho cuộc đối đầu giữa Alana và Prayogo và tay sai của họ, điều này đã đưa Alana đến số phận của cô."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"스리아시-사랑의 여신","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"화산 폭발로 인해 태어나자마자 친부모와 헤어진 알라나는 분노를 주체할 수 없다. 그녀를 입양한 부잣집 여인은 그녀를 보통 사람으로 키우려고 하지만 그녀는 성장할수록 자신이 보통 사람이 아님을 알게 된다. 그녀가 분노를 주체할 수 없는 순간 그녀는 인류에게 축복이 될 수도 재앙이 될 수도 있는 존재였던 것이다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Alana, déesse de justice","runtime":135,"tagline":"Bienvenue à l’incarnation de Dewi Asih...","homepage":"","overview":"Séparée de ses parents à la naissance suite à une éruption volcanique, puis ayant grandi dans une société très injuste, Alana tente de comprendre le mystère de ses crises de colère. Quand elle apprend qu'elle est la réincarnation de Sri Asih, la déesse de justice, elle va mettre ses super-pouvoirs au service du bien contre la corruption et le crime organisé."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"神奇女侠斯里阿西","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"斯里阿西与父母失散被一位富婆收养，当她成年后她发现了自己起源的真相。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Битва Богов","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Алана работает следователем и пытается прижать международную преступную группировку, а для этого ей приходится использовать волшебный боевой шарф и свою супергеройскую личность Шри Асих, способную призывать духов."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Queen of Justice - Sri Asih","runtime":135,"tagline":"Eine Legende wird geboren","homepage":"","overview":"Während eines Vulkanausbruchs geboren, bei dem ihre Eltern ums Leben kamen, wird Alana von einer Frau namens Sarita adoptiert. Unter ihrer Anleitung wächst das Mädchen zu einer beeindruckenden Kampfsportlerin heran. Als Erwachsene entdeckt Alana die Wahrheit über ihre Herkunft: Sie ist die Inkarnation der Göttin Dewi Asih, der Beschützerin der Menschheit. Und so tritt die Frau mit der Superpower gegen jene bösen Mächte an, die die Erde vernichten wollen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Quando ainda era bebê, Alana foi separada de seus pais e adotada por uma mulher rica. Ao atingir a maioridade, ela descobre que não é um ser humano qualquer e possui superpoderes. O futuro da humanidade agora depende da sua capacidade em controlar a própria raiva."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Inspirada en los cómics indonesios, Sri Asih cuenta la historia de Alana, una niña adoptada por una mujer rica después de perder a sus padres cuando aún era un bebé. Pero al alcanzar la mayoría de edad, descubre que es la reencarnación de la diosa Asih y que el futuro de la humanidad depende de su capacidad para controlar sus nuevos poderes."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Alana, déesse de justice","runtime":135,"tagline":"Bienvenue à l’incarnation de Dewi Asih...","homepage":"","overview":"Séparée de ses parents à la naissance suite à une éruption volcanique, puis ayant grandi dans une société très injuste, Alana tente de comprendre le mystère de ses crises de colère. Quand elle apprend qu'elle est la réincarnation de Sri Asih, la déesse de justice, elle va mettre ses super-pouvoirs au service du bien contre la corruption et le crime organisé."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Bir volkan patlaması sırasında doğan ve ebeveynleri bu esnada kaybeden Alana, Sarita adında bir kadın tarafından evlat edinilir. Sarita’nın önderliğinde, genç kız etkileyici bir dövüş sanatçısı olarak yetişir. Yetişkin olduğunda, Alana kökeni hakkındaki gerçeği keşfeder: O, insanlığın koruyucusu olan tanrıça Dewi Asih’in enkarnasyonudur. Böylece, süper güçlere sahip kadın, Dünya’yı yok etmek isteyen kötü güçlere karşı mücadele eder."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"最強女神覺醒了！","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"スリ・アシィ","runtime":0,"tagline":"最強の女神が目覚める","homepage":"https://sri-asih.com/","overview":"ジャワ島のムラピ山が噴火し、車で逃げ惑う若夫婦が事故で亡くなる。死の間際に生まれた女の子、アラナ(ペフィタ・ピアース)は、孤児院で正義感の強い少女に育つ。裕福な女性に引き取られ、成長したアラナは格闘家として活躍しながらも、激しい「怒り」に飲み込まれそうになることにいつも悩んでいた。そんなある日、トラブルに巻き込まれ養母が瀕死の重体に陥ってしまうが、アラナを見守ってきたという謎の組織に２人は助けられる。そして彼女は自らに秘められた運命を知ることとなり、伝説のヒーロー「スリ・アシィ」として火の女神の復活を阻止すべく戦うことを決心する…！怒りの誘惑と闘う彼女がもたらすのは、「救い」か、「破壊」か…。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Alana elszakadt a szüleitől, és egy gazdag nő fogadta örökbe. Felnőttkorában rájön az igazságra származásával kapcsolatban."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Alana","runtime":0,"tagline":"Diamo il benvenuto all'incarnazione di Dewi Asih...","homepage":"","overview":"Alana scopre la verità sulle sue origini: non è un essere umano normale. Potrebbe essere il dono per l'umanità e diventarne la protettrice come Sri Asih. O una distruzione, se non riesce a controllare la sua rabbia."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Sri Asih - Bogini sprawiedliwości","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kobieta będąca reinkarnacją Bogini Asih próbuje przywrócić porządek w społeczeństwie."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Alana ontdekt de waarheid over haar afkomst: ze is geen gewoon mens. Zij kan het geschenk voor de mensheid zijn en haar beschermer worden als Sri Asih. Of een vernietiger, als ze haar woede niet kan beheersen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Alana, diosa vengadora","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Esta película de acción, basada en una saga de cómics indonesios, sigue a Alana, una joven nacida durante una erupción volcánica que ha lidiado con problemas de ira desde su infancia. Su vida cambia cuando descubre que su furia tiene un origen sobrenatural vinculado al volcán que marcó su nacimiento."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"ศรี อาซิห์","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"อลาน่าไม่เข้าใจว่าทำไมเธอถึงถูกครอบงำด้วยความโกรธอยู่เสมอ แต่เธอก็พยายามต่อสู้กับมันอยู่เสมอ เธอเกิดระหว่างการปะทุของภูเขาไฟซึ่งทำให้เธอและพ่อแม่ของเธอต้องพรากจากกัน เธอเป็นลูกบุญธรรมโดยผู้หญิงรวยที่พยายามช่วยให้เธอใช้ชีวิตตามปกติ แต่เมื่อโตเป็นผู้ใหญ่ อลาน่าก็ค้นพบความจริงเกี่ยวกับต้นกำเนิดของเธอ เธอไม่ใช่มนุษย์ธรรมดา เธอสามารถเป็นคนดีได้ตลอดชีวิต หรือกลายเป็นความพินาศหากเธอไม่สามารถควบคุมความโกรธของเธอได้"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Dobrodošli v utelešenju Dewi Asih...","homepage":"","overview":"Alana odkrije resnico o svojem poreklu: ni navaden človek. Morda je darilo za človeštvo in postane njegova zaščitnica kot Sri Asih. Ali pa uničenje, če ne bo mogla nadzorovati svoje jeze."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1140817,"adult":false,"title":"As","video":false,"overview":"Three years after the death of her beloved child, Elouise, Mara still feels her presence when she sits on the butterfly bedding in front of the jar with her ashes in it. Mara arranges a twelfth birthday party for Elouise, further alienating her from her husband, Richter, and remaining daughter, Hannah. Although Mara eventually vacates Elouise's room at the insistence of her husband, she does find a way to stay close to Elouise. Before long, however, Hannah discovers her mother's secret.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2105,"vote_count":185,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2023-01-01","vote_average":7.054,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"As","original_language":"en"},{"id":444090,"adult":false,"title":"The Ash Lad: In the Hall of the Mountain King","video":false,"overview":"Espen “Ash Lad”, a poor farmer’s son, embarks on a dangerous quest with his brothers to save the princess from a vile troll known as the Mountain King – in order to collect a reward and save his family’s farm from ruin.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.952,"vote_count":401,"poster_path":"/uyJEfpAflLCkqn6PFHu9EHxmbI6.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-29","vote_average":6.772,"backdrop_path":"/iFMARpEJnSQBUDKzKvvRw6ATVF3.jpg","original_title":"Askeladden - I Dovregubbens hall","original_language":"no"},{"id":707933,"adult":false,"title":"Mendarat Darurat","video":false,"overview":"Glen was surprised when he accidentally cheated on death, with infidelity. Now the real problem is: How will he explain his luck to Maya, his wife?","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2869,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/wwftD9NgMl8fBec2tOaikUetZTW.jpg","release_date":"2022-09-08","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/klBiBaocChBAIkqxSQPwOJCsny0.jpg","original_title":"Mendarat Darurat","original_language":"id"},{"id":667062,"adult":false,"title":"Legend of Gatotkaca","video":false,"overview":"A young man discovers he is the descendant of a powerful warrior and must unlock his hidden abilities to fight an ancient enemy who seeks to alter history and destroy the world.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,14,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3819,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/tbx0zPMcbPlhGALf1XzAw3CzKMT.jpg","release_date":"2022-06-09","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/uMObsizFuj15a6fipOS8h6usVCq.jpg","original_title":"Satria Dewa: Gatotkaca","original_language":"id"},{"id":1006701,"adult":false,"title":"Under the Hanging Tree","video":false,"overview":"Christina Mureti, an impetuous police officer from the city, is transferred to a small desert town in Namibia where she uncovers a series of grizzly animal sacrifices. Then a German farmer is found hung on the same tree where Christina’s ancestors were hung a century ago during Germany’s colonial war with the Herero. Only when Christina begins to learn about her people’s history and embraces some of its cultural wisdom is she able to solve the case.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1365,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/lJXlOQEJZV9biJKzuq3Bub13mIE.jpg","release_date":"2023-01-25","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/pNT6QTeAhlK5S6X1LBlToiGV0g2.jpg","original_title":"Under the Hanging Tree","original_language":"af"},{"id":272069,"adult":false,"title":"Die Huberbuam - Close Call with Mount Asgard","video":false,"overview":"The climbing brothers Thomas and Alexander Huber (Germany) attempt to conquer free the infamous \"Bavarian Direttissima\" (upper tenth degree of difficulty) on the iconic Mt. Asgard on the Arctic Baffin Island (Canada). A 40 days expedition with polar bears, frostbite and climbing at the peril of their lifes.","genre_ids":[12,99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0698,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/dubGiFw72rpL98gQYFNuwf7WUxy.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-13","vote_average":4.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Die Huberbuam - Close Call with Mount Asgard","original_language":"de"},{"id":1001044,"adult":false,"title":"Drone","video":false,"overview":"Émilie lives in a world of surveillance: her camgirl work; the camera phone lingering on a crush from afar; the headset affording her a drone’s perspective. The same drone that stalks each move she makes, offering inspiration, noting rivals. An unsolicited companion is conspiring with or against her. A financially strapped transplant now living in the Paris suburbs, Émilie is thrust into a high-powered world when she is chosen for a renovation workshop with a prestigious architect. Her classmates come mostly from “filthy rich” backgrounds, like cocky Olivier, who wants Émilie as his conquest. But Émilie has shy eyes only for self-sufficient Mina, whose music builds like a “helicoid.” A drone—unlike any known model—is watching her all along waiting for her next move and paying handily for the privilege.","genre_ids":[18,10749,53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6774,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/flIYY0q6x5k6XpYSGtZz3hlOoBP.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-02","vote_average":5.286,"backdrop_path":"/cgOZCBWVp2MqYiBOfrcAb3p2NuN.jpg","original_title":"Drone","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1004255,"adult":false,"title":"Je ne suis pas un héros","video":false,"overview":"Louis is a super nice guy. But in his lawyer's office, this is not a compliment. When his doctor wrongly diagnoses a serious disease, his colleagues behaviour changes : they care about him, they ask him questions and they listen his answers. Finally, Louis exists ! So, obviously, he hesitates over telling the truth.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5576,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/qH8p6c3P7wruLcckGpxdoA0BrKG.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-22","vote_average":6.134,"backdrop_path":"/kIrboYJcV9fgvLLXOM9daBowLqI.jpg","original_title":"Je ne suis pas un héros","original_language":"fr"},{"id":43420,"adult":false,"title":"Cinema, Aspirins and Vultures","video":false,"overview":"1942, in the middle of Northeastern Brazil, two very different men meet along the road: Johan, an aspirin salesman avoiding the German draft, and Ranulpho, a rural Brazilian seeking escape from the drought.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3393,"vote_count":114,"poster_path":"/8lCLU3vMgauPutirtcbHDC3pRUI.jpg","release_date":"2005-05-17","vote_average":6.904,"backdrop_path":"/tnf0o78SWhaLqMgfdqhNwsPeDUW.jpg","original_title":"Cinema, Aspirinas e Urubus","original_language":"pt"},{"id":484428,"adult":false,"title":"Becoming Astrid","video":false,"overview":"When Astrid Lindgren was very young something happened that affected her profoundly, and this combination of both miracle and calamity came to shape her entire life. It was an event that transformed her into one of the most inspiring women of our age and the storyteller a whole world would come to love. This is the story of when a young Astrid, despite the expectations of her time and religious upbringing, decided to break free from society's norms and follow her heart.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.445,"vote_count":173,"poster_path":"/eEbu8tFPSyM4zt9dPJjeFj3qwlF.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-14","vote_average":7.023,"backdrop_path":"/mSjjzzuj87pJV3paZWBrtaro474.jpg","original_title":"Unga Astrid","original_language":"sv"},{"id":1046090,"adult":false,"title":"The Pig, the Snake and the Pigeon","video":false,"overview":"The arrogant, third most-wanted criminal in Taiwan, decides to get rid of the top two competitors and crowns himself the most-wanted criminal before dying.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8718,"vote_count":254,"poster_path":"/9FhZ9VC999qeOWH2ytbangUMMt4.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-06","vote_average":7.28,"backdrop_path":"/cu5Qk2QHxOyyMrD3Bq93DxgmJer.jpg","original_title":"周處除三害","original_language":"zh"},{"id":950526,"adult":false,"title":"The Smoke Master","video":false,"overview":"The journey of Gabriel and Daniel, two brothers cursed by the Chinese mafia with its feared Three Generations Revenge, who have already reaped the life of their grandfather and their father. To survive, one of the brothers must learn the Smoke Style secrets, a little known Cannabis martial art, taught by a single master, high up in the mountains.","genre_ids":[28,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6785,"vote_count":74,"poster_path":"/mg6YkwftQOJjpT2ygYlCi11LWeC.jpg","release_date":"2023-05-18","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/kwzNUM4yZ26XuNAPSyaWwJeWRP4.jpg","original_title":"O Mestre da Fumaça","original_language":"pt"},{"id":949429,"adult":false,"title":"The Adventures","video":false,"overview":"Joy, a secretary at a large multinational company, has an online shopping problem, likes to read adventure novels and watch travel and adventure shows. She daydreams about living a life of adventure.","genre_ids":[10749,35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8826,"vote_count":78,"poster_path":"/z3SeS4wjKQ3TjHSvRidovGJbHYb.jpg","release_date":"2023-12-22","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/mOQV573Tr0WxI2VVOLKwtfaRGZH.jpg","original_title":"ผจญภัยล่าขุมทรัพย์หมื่นลี้","original_language":"th"},{"id":763215,"adult":false,"title":"Damsel","video":false,"overview":"A young woman's marriage to a charming prince turns into a fierce fight for survival when she's offered up as a sacrifice to a fire-breathing dragon.","genre_ids":[14,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.2017,"vote_count":2700,"poster_path":"/AgHbB9DCE9aE57zkHjSmseszh6e.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-07","vote_average":6.